overview: On the final stop on Brock Lesnar's Go to Hell Tour, the Beast sets out to lay his storied rivalry with The Undertaker to rest inside the demonic Hell in a Cell. Plus, Roman Reigns looks to settle a score with Bray Wyatt inside the Cell, WWE World Heavyweight Champion Seth Rollins puts it all on the line against Kane, and much more.
title: WWE Hell in a Cell 2015
